{"tid":1421850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣入] 文宣需要緊急進化","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:57:50.000Z","uid":148709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a37e759e1eb5179d681d97d9e51c0e5a50c40ff","tid":1421850,"uid":148709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:06:45.000Z","msg":"進化分線係每日狗會<br />\n呢個狗會係對家文宣武器<br />\n特點係：<br />\n1. 放大我地做嘅嘢<br />\n2. 利用cctvb大台優點<br />\n3. 製造fake news/誤導news<br />\n<br />\n針對每日狗會我哋要更新文宣戰略<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔主動回應每日狗會內容，文宣唔可以變被動，我地好難守<br />\n2. 跟風戰略，放大對家錯處，特別係道德觀感嘅事(例如性侵少女) 唔好放大同回應自己做錯嘅事(例如扔嘢唔夠力failed)  我哋要主動提出佢哋唔跟法例嘅行為(例如私刑，亂開槍)<br />\n3. 指出同提醒市民佢哋使用嘅過度武力(例如插眼，射頭射眼，屈手，打路過街坊)<br />\n4. 圖片方面放大我哋幫助在場市民嘅相<br />\n(例如下圖) <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppFzUDq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FppFzUDq.jpg&h=7a4fed77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b0d627351df5a5e37ac15fe0a9436155d36f642","tid":1421850,"uid":148709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:09:47.000Z","msg":"自up"},{"pid":"5ad4a9f0db8b5d19a0734e7768a9bc7001544c21","tid":1421850,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"推晒所有機場post<br />\n機場好重要<br />\n絕對係一個大既國際新聞<br />\n8月9-11日<br />\n和理非進場<br />\n唔好比港共轉移視線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFeQsAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFeQsAz.jpg&h=ead62688&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"292893822fc4b53f87cf974395d5035c1b0b1d5c","tid":1421850,"uid":148709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"自up"},{"pid":"ca787408542ddcf917c9f53fd32665ac4a7457fc","tid":1421850,"uid":148709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"自up"}]}